Description:
    Creates a new Angular controller

Example:
    yo angular:controller Thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by component):
        app/scripts/controllers/thing-ctrl.js

    or (division by feature):
    	app/src/common/controllers/thing-ctrl.js


    yo angular:controller foo/Thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/controllers/thing-ctrl.js


    yo angular:controller foo/bar/Thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/bar/controllers/thing-ctrl.js
